  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Non-cannulated pedicle screw compression-bending credibility assessment (Minimal Profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for FEA prediction of ASTM F1717 static compression-bending performance of a non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct. This model has been applied in clinical research evaluating spinal implant safety margins, and the ensemble FEA approach (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) has been compared against N=11 experimental constructs across two independent laboratories. All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors have been assessed; one factor (Test conditions) falls below the required level due to evaluation under a single test condition. The package is filed under the Minimal profile; structured context-of-use scope is documented in accompanying laboratory records.",
